# Design System

## Brand Colors
```css
/* Marriott / Bonvoy palette */
--bonvoy-red:     #C8102E;   /* Primary brand red — CTAs, badges */
--bonvoy-dark:    #1A1A2E;   /* Dark navy — headers, nav */
--bonvoy-gold:    #B8962E;   /* Gold — loyalty tier accents, badges */

/* Eco colors */
--eco-green:      #22c55e;   /* Score ≥ 7 */
--eco-yellow:     #eab308;   /* Score 5–6.9 */
--eco-red:        #ef4444;   /* Score < 5 */

/* Neutrals */
--surface:        #FFFFFF;
--surface-subtle: #F8F9FA;
--border:         #E5E7EB;
--text-primary:   #111827;
--text-muted:     #6B7280;
```

In Tailwind config, map these as custom colors.

## Typography
- Headings: `font-bold` tracking-tight
- Body: default Inter (Tailwind base)
- Accessibility font toggle: applies `font-dyslexic` class to `<body>` via OpenDyslexic

## Card Design Pattern
All cards use this base:
```tsx
<div className="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
```
No sharp corners anywhere in the UI. Minimum `rounded-xl` on all cards.

## Buttons
- Primary: `bg-[#C8102E] text-white hover:bg-[#a50d26] rounded-full px-6 py-3`
- Secondary: `border border-[#C8102E] text-[#C8102E] rounded-full px-6 py-3`
- Ghost: `text-[#C8102E] underline-offset-2 hover:underline`

## Bottom Navigation (Mobile)
4 tabs: Home (search), Stays, Map/Explore, Profile
Use sticky bottom nav on mobile (`fixed bottom-0`).

## Accessibility Modes
Toggle stored in localStorage as `a11y_mode`:
```ts
type A11yMode = {
  high_contrast: boolean;
  dyslexia_font: boolean;
  reduced_motion: boolean;
  large_touch: boolean; // adds extra padding to all interactive elements
}
```
Apply as CSS classes on `<html>` element. Never use inline styles for a11y modes.

## Loading States
- Skeleton screens only (no spinners) — use shadcn/ui `Skeleton` component
- Eco ring: show grey skeleton ring while loading

## Empty States
Every list/section must have a friendly empty state:
```tsx
<div className="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 py-10 text-gray-400">
  <Icon className="w-10 h-10" />
  <p className="text-sm">No [items] yet.</p>
</div>
```

## Map Styling
- Use `mapbox://styles/mapbox/streets-v12` — clean, readable
- Partner markers: colored circles (12px) with white border
- Selected marker: larger (16px) with shadow
- Bottom sheet slides up with `transition-transform duration-300`
